WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.266 --> 00:00:01.100
Nonsense,

2
00:00:01.100 --> 00:00:02.633
You were the one who cheated first.

3
00:00:02.766 --> 00:00:02.900
You...

4
00:00:03.833 --> 00:00:04.166
Guess what?

5
00:00:04.166 --> 00:00:05.633
If Zhi Han said right now

6
00:00:05.633 --> 00:00:06.600
he wants to be with his dad,

7
00:00:07.666 --> 00:00:09.900
who do you think the court would give him to?

8
00:00:11.800 --> 00:00:12.400
That's right.

9
00:00:12.800 --> 00:00:13.866
It's time for dinner.

10
00:00:13.866 --> 00:00:16.366
We'll talk about Zhi Han after we eat.

11
00:00:17.300 --> 00:00:17.733
Let's go.

12
00:00:27.166 --> 00:00:28.700
You're a bad mom.

13
00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:30.400
I hate you.

14
00:00:36.533 --> 00:00:37.700
Some people

15
00:00:37.700 --> 00:00:38.966
really have no shame,

16
00:00:39.300 --> 00:00:40.566
even during dinner time.

17
00:00:41.333 --> 00:00:41.966
Really...

18
00:00:42.866 --> 00:00:44.000
Don't be angry, Auntie.

19
00:00:44.300 --> 00:00:45.133
Maybe Jian Dao

20
00:00:45.133 --> 00:00:46.466
just wanted to visit you.

21
00:00:47.800 --> 00:00:48.600
Visit me?

22
00:00:49.566 --> 00:00:51.666
If she looked at me even once,

23
00:00:51.966 --> 00:00:53.700
I'd probably lose half a year of life.

24
00:00:55.300 --> 00:00:56.866
Then I should look at you more,

25
00:00:57.333 --> 00:00:58.566
to make sure by next year

26
00:00:58.566 --> 00:01:00.300
you and your husband can be reunited.

27
00:01:00.866 --> 00:01:01.666
How dare you speak like that!
